<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Documentation | Kharat Bot</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/docs.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/navbar.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.6.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class = "container">

    <%- include("partials/navbar") %>

    <main class="docs-page">

        <header class="hero">
            <h1>Documentation</h1>
            <p>
                 configure and use Kharat Bot.
                This documentation will continue to expand and will be more organized with future updates.
            </p>
        </header>

        <section>
            <h2>Getting Started</h2>

            <ol>
                <li>Invite Kharat Bot to your Discord server.</li>
                <li>Grant Admin permissions.(more options in future)</li>
                <li>Configure command prefix. (default is : "<strong>,</strong>")</li>
                <li>Make sure bot role is high enough </li>
            </ol>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Basic Commands</h2>

            <ul>
                <li><strong>ban</strong> — Permanently bans a member.</li>
                <li><strong>kick</strong> — Removes a member.</li>
                <li><strong>timeout</strong> — Temporarily mutes a member.</li>
                <li><strong>gulag</strong> — Sends a member to the Gulag.</li>
                <li><strong>forgive</strong> — Removes the Gulag punishment.</li>
                <li><strong>prefix</strong> — Shows current prefix .</li>
                <li><strong>cgprefix</strong> — Change the current prefix.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Configuration</h2>

            <p>Configure the moderation system before using jail system </p>

            <ul>
                <li><strong>gulagrole</strong> — Sets the Gulag role.</li>
                <li><strong>gulagchannelid</strong> — Sets the Gulag channel.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Permissions</h2>

            <p>
                moderation commands require appropriate Discord permissions.
                Make sure the bot role is above the member's role you trying to make action on .
            </p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

            <h3>How do I change the prefix?</h3>
            <p>Use the <strong>cgprefix</strong> command.</p>

            <h3>Why can't the bot ban members?</h3>
            <p>Ensure the bot has the Ban Members permission and its role is higher than the target member.</p>

            <h3>Is bot dashboard available ?</h3>
            <p>Dashboard for configuring server setting will be available in next update .</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>More Documentation Coming Soon</h2>

            <p>
                Future releases will include detailed commands information .
            </p>
        </section>

    </main>
    </div>

</body>
</html>